    "meaning": "English tenses show more than just time (Past, Present, Future). They also show the situation or 'aspect'—whether an action is simple, ongoing, completed, or continuing. Understanding this system makes learning individual tenses much easier.",
    "explanation": "\n      <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-2\">The Two Big Ideas</h4>\n      <p>To understand tenses, you only need to combine two concepts:</p>\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-4\">\n        <div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n          <strong class=\"text-emerald-400 block mb-2\">1. Time Area (When?)</strong>\n          <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-slate-300\">\n            <li><strong>Present:</strong> Connected to now</li>\n            <li><strong>Past:</strong> Before now</li>\n            <li><strong>Future:</strong> After now</li>\n            <li><strong>Past Future:</strong> Future from a past point of view</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n          <strong class=\"text-blue-400 block mb-2\">2. Action Type (How/Aspect?)</strong>\n          <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-slate-300\">\n            <li><strong>Simple:</strong> Fact, habit, or general event</li>\n            <li><strong>Continuous:</strong> Action in progress</li>\n            <li><strong>Perfect:</strong> Action connected to another time</li>\n            <li><strong>Perfect Continuous:</strong> Duration connected to another time</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">Timeline Explanation</h4>\n      <p>Imagine a straight line representing time. <strong>Present</strong> is right now. <strong>Past</strong> is behind you. <strong>Future</strong> is ahead of you. <strong>Past Future</strong> is looking ahead while standing in the past.</p>\n      <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-6 text-slate-300\">\n        <li><strong>Present:</strong> I study every day.</li>\n        <li><strong>Past:</strong> I studied yesterday.</li>\n        <li><strong>Future:</strong> I will study tomorrow.</li>\n        <li><strong>Past Future:</strong> I said I would study later.</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">Aspect Comparison (Action Types)</h4>\n      <p>Let's look at the verb \"study\" across the four action types in the Present time area to see how the meaning changes:</p>\n      <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-6 text-slate-300\">\n        <li><strong>Simple:</strong> I study English. <em>(General fact or habit)</em></li>\n        <li><strong>Continuous:</strong> I am studying English. <em>(Happening right now, in progress)</em></li>\n        <li><strong>Perfect:</strong> I have studied English. <em>(Experience or finished action connected to now)</em></li>\n        <li><strong>Perfect Continuous:</strong> I have been studying English. <em>(Duration, started in the past and still ongoing)</em></li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-4\">16 Tenses Overview Chart</h4>\n      <div class=\"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-700 mb-8\">\n        <table class=\"w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[600px]\">\n          <thead>\n            <tr class=\"bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n              <th class=\"p-3 border-b border-r border-slate-700\">Action Type &rarr;<br>Time Area &darr;</th>\n              <th class=\"p-3 border-b border-r border-slate-700 text-emerald-400\">Simple</th>\n              <th class=\"p-3 border-b border-r border-slate-700 text-blue-400\">Continuous</th>\n              <th class=\"p-3 border-b border-r border-slate-700 text-purple-400\">Perfect</th>\n              <th class=\"p-3 border-b border-slate-700 text-orange-400\">Perfect Cont.</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody class=\"text-sm\">\n            <tr class=\"border-b border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50\">\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700 font-bold text-slate-200\">Present</td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Habit/Fact</strong><br>V1 / V1+s<br><em>I study</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>In Progress Now</strong><br>am/is/are + V-ing<br><em>I am studying</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Finished/Experience</strong><br>have/has + V3<br><em>I have studied</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3\"><strong>Duration to Now</strong><br>have/has been + V-ing<br><em>I have been studying</em></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"border-b border-slate-700\">\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700 font-bold text-slate-200\">Past</td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Finished Past</strong><br>V2<br><em>I studied</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>In Progress Past</strong><br>was/were + V-ing<br><em>I was studying</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Before Past Action</strong><br>had + V3<br><em>I had studied</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3\"><strong>Duration to Past</strong><br>had been + V-ing<br><em>I had been studying</em></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr class=\"border-b border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50\">\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700 font-bold text-slate-200\">Future</td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Prediction/Plan</strong><br>will + V1<br><em>I will study</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>In Progress Future</strong><br>will be + V-ing<br><em>I will be studying</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Finished Before Future</strong><br>will have + V3<br><em>I will have studied</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3\"><strong>Duration to Future</strong><br>will have been + V-ing<br><em>I will have been studying</em></td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700 font-bold text-slate-200\">Past Future</td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Future from Past</strong><br>would + V1<br><em>I would study</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>In Progress Later (Past View)</strong><br>would be + V-ing<br><em>I would be studying</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3 border-r border-slate-700\"><strong>Finished Later (Past View)</strong><br>would have + V3<br><em>I would have studied</em></td>\n              <td class=\"p-3\"><strong>Duration Later (Past View)</strong><br>would have been + V-ing<br><em>I would have been studying</em></td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n    ",
